      "items": [
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Colorado, USA"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Food and Beverage"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "51-200 Employees"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "The Customer"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "The client, a leading third-party food verification company headquartered in Colorado, employs around 89 people and generates an annual revenue of over $25 million. They ensure the accuracy of food production claims through comprehensive verification and certification services. By providing rigorous auditing and certification processes, the client supports various stakeholders in the food industry, including farmers, processors, retailers, and restaurants, in maintaining high standards of food safety and sustainability​"
        }
      ],
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Colorado, USA"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Food and Beverage"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "51-200 Employees"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "The Customer"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "The client, a leading third-party food verification company headquartered in Colorado, employs around 89 people and generates an annual revenue of over $25 million. They ensure the accuracy of food production claims through comprehensive verification and certification services. By providing rigorous auditing and certification processes, the client supports various stakeholders in the food industry, including farmers, processors, retailers, and restaurants, in maintaining high standards of food safety and sustainability​"
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "items": [
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "The Problem"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Manual updates mean that decision-makers may not have access to real-time data."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Large Excel files can slow down the performance of Power BI reports and dashboards."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Manually updating the data can be time-consuming and inefficient."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Without secure connections, there is an increased risk of unauthorized access to sensitive data."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Manual handling of Excel files increases the risk of errors such as accidental deletions or incorrect data entry."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Without automation, the process of data collection, updating, and reporting is manual and prone to delays."
        }
      ],
      "headings": [
        {
